New Records: Shohei Ohtani reached his 56th stolen base of the season and drove in the go-ahead run in the sixth inning
Los Angeles Dodgers moved within one win of clinching the NL West
Key Match Events: Shohei Ohtani singled in the go-ahead run before stealing his 56th base of the season in the sixth inning
Fernando Tatis Jr. homered to left center (448 feet) in the fifth inning
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was played at Dodger Stadium with an attendance of 52,310
